2. Analyze prompt injection and jailbreak attack surfaces.
3. Assess RAG pipelines, retrieval mechanisms, and vector databases.
4. Evaluate model supply chain and serialization security.
5. Scan models for malicious payloads and unsafe architectures.
6. Assess AI-specific threats including poisoning and sensitive data exposure.
7. Validate layered security controls and deployment protections.
8. Recommend defense-in-depth strategies aligned with OWASP LLM Top 10.

